# Nitro-Craft

Nitro-Craft is the dedicated home for **NitroCraft**.

NitroCraft is a fast Minecraft API for avatars, skins, capes, and renders, with UUID/username tooling, status utilities, and production-focused caching.

## NitroCraft

- Repository: [NitroCraft](https://github.com/EuphoriaDevelopmentOrg/NitroCraft)
- Live docs/home: [nitrocraft.uk](https://nitrocraft.uk)
- Discord: [discord.euphoriadevelopment.uk](https://discord.euphoriadevelopment.uk)

## What NitroCraft Provides

- Avatar, skin, cape, and render endpoints
- UUID and username player resolution
- Java/Bedrock status endpoints
- OpenAPI + metrics endpoints
- Built-in caching and rate-limit controls
- Server-list preview tooling

## Main Endpoints

- `/avatars/{uuid}`
- `/skins/{uuid}`
- `/capes/{uuid}`
- `/renders/head/{uuid}`
- `/renders/body/{uuid}`
- `/players/{uuid-or-username}`
- `/status/server`
- `/openapi.json`
- `/metrics`

